This paper is about using generative adversarial networks (GANs) to generate high-resolution medical images. The paper focuses on the technical details of the approach, which involves progressively growing the GAN to generate higher resolution images. Given the focus on computer vision and machine learning, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
